reviews.content:
I wanted to share my experience with Coterie. I subscribed through their website &amp; ordered my first package before my baby arrived, which included several packs of diapers in size N &amp; wipes. After my baby’s arrival, I noticed right away how great Coterie was no rashes at all, &amp; I loved that the material was free from plastic.
However, within just 3 hours I noticed the diapers were leaking. I reached out to Coterie, &amp; they instantly responded. Not only did they resolve the issue, but they also credited me for the remaining packs. They even suggested trying a bigger size, &amp; my first package included a trial pack of the next size up, which worked perfectly for my baby. I’ve now placed my second order with them in the bigger size, &amp; I’m so happy with the results. I really appreciate how helpful &amp; 
responsive their team was in solving my concern. I would highly recommend Coterie to every parent 💕
